snippet.title: Revolution: The Spark Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Revolution: The Spark, a story-driven, turn-based role-playing game about revolution of the masses in alternative Steampunk world. Coming out on Steam (Early Access) in Q3 2020!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1334230/Revolution_The_Spark/

Facebook - https://facebook.com/TheSparkGame
Instagram - https://instagram.com/thesparkwebtoon
Twitter - https://twitter.com/TheSparkGame
Discord - https://discord.gg/F28jzvQ
